{"tid":906104,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇啲一諗起就流眼淚嘅畫面？","createTime":"2018-11-17T16:38:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-17T19:02:36.000Z","uid":158767,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e95392812bc1d4b245d9069f08b64f372aea7ab9","tid":906104,"uid":158767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T16:38:06.000Z","msg":"同個鐘意咗好耐嘅囡仔睇完戲，食完飯，<br />\n同佢行去搭車，咁我地傾計，<br />\n佢話佢買咗個結他學，但係隻手好細會好難學，<br />\n跟住我就諗住拼隻手去佢隻手度下差幾大，<br />\n結果佢以為我想拖佢，跟住縮手。<br />\n一諗起個佢縮手個畫面，對眼就自動標啲眼淚出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 a09"},{"pid":"6861de2dce4aac42b977ac7862601c14b80a64c3","tid":906104,"uid":107408,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T16:49:38.000Z","msg":"返工做狗"},{"pid":"a306fce3200de90c9dee0d793b44e7a5b11d4366","tid":906104,"uid":101743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T16:51:45.000Z","msg":"樓主好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"511d4858c3ff302dffd7cb9de5f539e59a32ac3b","tid":906104,"uid":158767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a306fce3200de90c9dee0d793b44e7a5b11d4366","tid":906104,"uid":101743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T16:51:45.000Z","msg":"樓主好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T16:54:19.000Z","msg":"一路以為自己有機會，原來諗多咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"313d447e89573bf8ff37977dc28f75969d7c29c6","tid":906104,"uid":43575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T17:23:36.000Z","msg":"97回歸直播，每次睇都會喊"},{"pid":"1936a7a29f2118b3094351d9ce3b016e94b9a7d1","tid":906104,"uid":199016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T17:27:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"16196c0e916912973769d34487925d6eaf3db041","tid":906104,"uid":199016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17